<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
<title>{{ date }} 장전 브리핑 · k-ant-daily</title>
<meta name="description" content="{{ tldr }}">
<link rel="canonical" href="{{ canonical_url }}">

<meta property="og:type" content="article">
<meta property="og:title" content="{{ date }} 장전 브리핑">
<meta property="og:description" content="{{ tldr }}">
<meta property="og:url" content="{{ canonical_url }}">
<meta property="og:locale" content="ko_KR">
<meta property="og:site_name" content="k-ant-daily">
<meta property="article:published_time" content="{{ generated_at }}">

<meta name="twitter:card" content="summary">
<meta name="twitter:title" content="{{ date }} 장전 브리핑">
<meta name="twitter:description" content="{{ tldr }}">

<style>
  :root {
    --fg: #0f172a;
    --muted: #64748b;
    --bg: #ffffff;
    --accent: #0f766e;
    --border: #e2e8f0;
    --card: #f8fafc;
    --pos: #dc2626;        /* 한국 주식 관행: 상승=빨강 */
    --pos-bg: rgba(220,38,38,0.08);
    --neg: #2563eb;        /* 하락=파랑 */
    --neg-bg: rgba(37,99,235,0.08);
    --neu: #6b7280;
    --neu-bg: rgba(107,114,128,0.08);
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    :root {
      --fg: #e2e8f0; --muted: #94a3b8; --bg: #0f172a; --accent: #5eead4;
      --border: #1e293b; --card: #1e293b;
      --pos: #f87171; --pos-bg: rgba(248,113,113,0.12);
      --neg: #60a5fa; --neg-bg: rgba(96,165,250,0.12);
      --neu: #94a3b8; --neu-bg: rgba(148,163,184,0.12);
    }
  }
  * { box-sizing: border-box; }
  html, body { margin: 0; padding: 0; background: var(--bg); color: var(--fg); }
  body {
    font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Apple SD Gothic Neo",
      "Pretendard", "Noto Sans KR", sans-serif;
    line-height: 1.6; font-size: 16px;
    -webkit-text-size-adjust: 100%;
  }
  main { max-width: 720px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 24px 20px 64px; }

  header { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); padding-bottom: 16px; margin-bottom: 24px; }
  header h1 { font-size: 24px; margin: 0 0 8px; letter-spacing: -0.01em; }
  header .tldr { margin: 0; color: var(--fg); font-size: 17px; font-weight: 500; }
  header time { display: block; color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 8px; }

  section { margin-bottom: 32px; }
  section > h2 { font-size: 18px; margin: 0 0 12px; display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px; }

  /* TOP STORIES */
  .top-stories {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--card), transparent);
    border: 1px solid var(--border); border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }

  /* FOCUS (geopolitics / hot topic) */
  .focus {
    background: var(--neg-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--neg); border-left: 4px solid var(--neg);
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 16px 18px; margin-bottom: 24px;
  }
  .focus h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .focus .focus-summary { margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 15px; }
  .focus-status {
    display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; gap: 8px 12px;
    padding: 10px 12px; margin: 0 0 12px;
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
  }
  .status-badge {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    font-size: 13px; font-weight: 700; padding: 4px 12px;
    border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .status-badge.closed      { background: #dc2626; color: white; }
  .status-badge.restricted  { background: #f59e0b; color: white; }
  .status-badge.open        { background: #16a34a; color: white; }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .status-badge.closed     { background: #b91c1c; }
    .status-badge.restricted { background: #d97706; }
    .status-badge.open       { background: #15803d; }
  }
  .status-detail { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .ship-count   { font-size: 13px; color: var(--fg); }
  .ship-count strong { font-size: 15px; color: var(--accent); }

  .news-items { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 8px 0 0; }
  .news-items li {
    padding: 10px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .news-items li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .news-items .headline { font-weight: 600; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .news-items .headline a { color: var(--fg); text-decoration: none; flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .news-items .headline a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .news-items .meta { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 3px; }
  .news-items .meta .dot { margin: 0 6px; }
  .news-items .time-ago { color: var(--accent); font-weight: 600; }
  .news-items .summary { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin-top: 4px; }

  /* COFFEE BANNER */
  .coffee-banner {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #fde68a 0%, #fbbf24 100%);
    color: #422006;
    border-radius: 12px; padding: 14px 18px; margin-bottom: 20px;
    font-size: 15px;
  }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .coffee-banner { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #78350f 0%, #92400e 100%); color: #fef3c7; }
  }
  .coffee-banner .headline { font-weight: 700; font-size: 17px; margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .coffee-banner .sub { font-size: 13px; opacity: 0.85; }
  .coffee-banner.none { background: var(--card); color: var(--fg); border: 1px dashed var(--border); }
  .friend-row { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px 10px; margin-top: 6px; font-size: 13px; }
  .friend-row .friend { display: inline-flex; gap: 4px; align-items: baseline; }
  .friend-row .friend .owner { font-weight: 600; }
  .friend-row .up { color: var(--pos); font-weight: 600; }
  .friend-row .down { color: var(--neg); font-weight: 600; }
  .friend-row .flat { color: var(--muted); }
  .top-stories h2 { margin-top: 0; }
  .top-stories ol { margin: 0; padding-left: 20px; }
  .top-stories li { padding: 8px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border); }
  .top-stories li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .top-stories .title { font-weight: 600; }
  .top-stories .why { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-top: 2px; }
  .top-stories .sources { margin-top: 6px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .top-stories .sources a {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--bg); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* IMPACT BADGES */
  .impact { display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; font-weight: 600; vertical-align: middle; margin-left: 6px; }
  .impact.positive { background: var(--pos-bg); color: var(--pos); }
  .impact.negative { background: var(--neg-bg); color: var(--neg); }
  .impact.neutral { background: var(--neu-bg); color: var(--neu); }

  /* INDICATORS */
  .indicators { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(140px, 1fr)); gap: 8px; margin-bottom: 12px; }
  .indicator { padding: 12px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid var(--border); background: var(--card); position: relative; }
  .indicator.positive { border-left: 3px solid var(--pos); background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--pos-bg), var(--card) 60%); }
  .indicator.negative { border-left: 3px solid var(--neg); background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--neg-bg), var(--card) 60%); }
  .indicator.neutral { border-left: 3px solid var(--neu); }
  .indicator .name { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: 4px; }
  .indicator .value { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
  .indicator .change { font-size: 13px; margin-top: 2px; font-weight: 500; }
  .indicator .change.up { color: var(--pos); }
  .indicator .change.down { color: var(--neg); }
  .indicator .arrow { font-size: 11px; margin-right: 2px; }
  .section-sub { font-size: 14px; color: var(--muted); margin: -4px 0 8px; }

  /* KEY POINTS */
  .summary { color: var(--fg); }
  .macro-mood {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 6px;
    font-size: 13px; padding: 4px 10px; border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 500;
    margin-left: 8px;
  }
  .macro-mood.positive { background: var(--pos-bg); color: var(--pos); }
  .macro-mood.negative { background: var(--neg-bg); color: var(--neg); }
  .macro-mood.neutral { background: var(--neu-bg); color: var(--neu); }

  .points { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .points li { padding: 12px 0; border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  .points li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .points .point-title { font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px; display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }
  .points .point-title .text { flex: 1; min-width: 0; }
  .points .point-detail { color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin: 4px 0; }
  .points .sources { margin-top: 6px; display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }
  .points .sources a {
    font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent); text-decoration: none;
    background: var(--card); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  .points .sources a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }

  /* STOCK CARD */
  article.stock { background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 12px; margin-bottom: 10px; overflow: hidden; }
  article.stock > details > summary {
    list-style: none; cursor: pointer; padding: 14px 16px;
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; flex-wrap: wrap;
    user-select: none;
  }
  article.stock > details > summary::-webkit-details-marker { display: none; }
  article.stock > details > summary::after {
    content: "▸"; color: var(--muted); font-size: 14px; margin-left: auto; transition: transform 0.15s;
  }
  article.stock > details[open] > summary::after { transform: rotate(90deg); }
  article.stock > details[open] > summary { border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border); }
  article.stock .body { padding: 12px 16px 16px; }
  article.stock .owner-tag {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent);
    background: var(--bg); padding: 3px 8px; border-radius: 999px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
  }
  article.stock .name { font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600; }
  article.stock .code { font-size: 11px; color: var(--muted); font-weight: 400; font-family: ui-monospace, SFMono-Regular, monospace; }
  article.stock .price-change {
    font-size: 15px; font-weight: 700; font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
    padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px;
  }
  article.stock .price-change.up { color: var(--pos); background: var(--pos-bg); }
  article.stock .price-change.down { color: var(--neg); background: var(--neg-bg); }
  article.stock .price-change.flat { color: var(--muted); background: var(--neu-bg); }
  article.stock header { border: none; padding: 0; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  article.stock h3 { margin: 0; font-size: 17px; display: flex; align-items: baseline; gap: 8px; flex-wrap: wrap; }

  /* RECOMMENDATION BADGE (5 levels) */
  .rec {
    display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 4px;
    font-size: 12px; font-weight: 700; padding: 3px 10px;
    border-radius: 999px; letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }
  .rec.strong_buy { background: #dc2626; color: white; }
  .rec.buy { background: var(--pos-bg); color: var(--pos); border: 1px solid var(--pos); }
  .rec.hold { background: var(--neu-bg); color: var(--neu); border: 1px solid var(--neu); }
  .rec.sell { background: var(--neg-bg); color: var(--neg); border: 1px solid var(--neg); }
  .rec.strong_sell { background: #1d4ed8; color: white; }
  @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) {
    .rec.strong_buy { background: #b91c1c; }
    .rec.strong_sell { background: #1e40af; }
  }
  .rec-rationale { color: var(--muted); font-size: 13px; margin-top: 6px; font-style: italic; }

  article.stock .stock-summary { margin: 8px 0 12px; }
  article.stock h4 { font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted); margin: 16px 0 8px; font-weight: 600; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; }

  /* DEEP DIVE */
  .deep-dive {
    background: var(--bg); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 12px 14px; margin-top: 12px; font-size: 14px;
  }
  .deep-dive h4 { margin-top: 0; }
  .deep-dive .dd-block { margin: 8px 0; }
  .deep-dive .dd-label { font-size: 11px; font-weight: 700; color: var(--accent); text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 0.05em; margin-bottom: 2px; }
  .deep-dive .dd-body { color: var(--fg); }
  .deep-dive .dd-tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 4px; margin-top: 4px; }
  .deep-dive .dd-tag { font-size: 11px; background: var(--card); padding: 2px 8px; border-radius: 4px; color: var(--muted); border: 1px solid var(--border); }

  .disclosures { list-style: none; padding: 0; margin: 0; }
  .disclosures li { font-size: 13px; padding: 6px 0; border-bottom: 1px dashed var(--border); }
  .disclosures li:last-child { border-bottom: none; }
  .disclosures a { color: var(--fg); text-decoration: none; }
  .disclosures a:hover { color: var(--accent); }
  .disclosures .date { color: var(--muted); font-size: 11px; margin-left: 6px; }

  .sector-tag { display: inline-block; font-size: 11px; background: var(--border); color: var(--muted); padding: 2px 6px; border-radius: 4px; margin-right: 4px; }

  footer {
    margin-top: 48px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--muted); font-size: 12px; text-align: center;
  }
  footer .disclaimer {
    background: var(--card); border: 1px solid var(--border); border-radius: 8px;
    padding: 10px 14px; margin-bottom: 10px; text-align: left;
  }
</style>
</head>
<body>
<main>
  <header>
    <h1>📰 {{ date }} 장전 브리핑</h1>
    <p class="tldr">{{ tldr }}</p>
    <time>생성: {{ generated_at_display }} KST · <a href="archive.html">아카이브</a></time>
  </header>

  {% if friends_overview %}
    {% if coffee_buyer %}
    <div class="coffee-banner">
      <div class="headline">☕ 오늘 커피는 <strong>{{ coffee_buyer.owner }}</strong>님이!</div>
      <div class="sub">{{ coffee_buyer.name }} {{ coffee_buyer.change_display }} — 친구 보유 종목 중 최고 상승</div>
      <div class="friend-row">
        {% for f in friends_overview %}
        <span class="friend"><span class="owner">{{ f.owner }}</span>·{{ f.name }} <span class="{{ f.direction or 'flat' }}">{{ f.change_display }}</span></span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% else %}
    <div class="coffee-banner none">
      <div class="headline">☕ 오늘 커피는 각자 사기</div>
      <div class="sub">친구 보유 종목 중 상승 종목 없음</div>
      <div class="friend-row">
        {% for f in friends_overview %}
        <span class="friend"><span class="owner">{{ f.owner }}</span>·{{ f.name }} <span class="{{ f.direction or 'flat' }}">{{ f.change_display }}</span></span>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
    {% endif %}
  {% endif %}

  {% if top_stories %}
  <section class="top-stories">
    <h2>⭐ 오늘의 핵심</h2>
    <ol>
      {% for ts in top_stories %}
      <li>
        <div class="title">
          <span>{{ ts.headline }}</span>
          {% if ts.impact %}<span class="impact {{ ts.impact }}">{{ ts.impact_label or ts.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if ts.why_it_matters %}<div class="why">{{ ts.why_it_matters }}</div>{% endif %}
        {% if ts.sources %}
        <div class="sources">
          {% for src in ts.sources %}<a href="{{ src.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ src.title }}</a>{% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ol>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% if focus %}
  <section class="focus">
    <h2>
      🚨 {{ focus.title or '집중 이슈' }}
      {% if focus.impact %}<span class="impact {{ focus.impact }}">{{ focus.impact_label or focus.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
    </h2>
    {% if focus.status %}
    <div class="focus-status">
      {% if focus.status.level %}
      <span class="status-badge {{ focus.status.level }}">
        {% if focus.status.level == 'closed' %}🚫{% elif focus.status.level == 'restricted' %}⚠️{% elif focus.status.level == 'open' %}✅{% endif %}
        {{ focus.status.label or focus.status.level }}
      </span>
      {% endif %}
      {% if focus.status.detail %}<span class="status-detail">{{ focus.status.detail }}</span>{% endif %}
      {% if focus.status.ship_count %}
      <span class="ship-count">
        🚢 <strong>{{ focus.status.ship_count.value }}</strong>
        {% if focus.status.ship_count.date %}({{ focus.status.ship_count.date }}){% endif %}
        {% if focus.status.ship_count.note %} · {{ focus.status.ship_count.note }}{% endif %}
        {% if focus.status.ship_count.source %}
        <a href="{{ focus.status.ship_count.source.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="color: var(--accent); margin-left: 4px;">({{ focus.status.ship_count.source.title }})</a>
        {% endif %}
      </span>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endif %}
    {% if focus.summary %}<p class="focus-summary">{{ focus.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if focus.news_items %}
    <ul class="news-items">
      {% for n in focus.news_items %}
      <li>
        <div class="headline">
          <a href="{{ n.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ n.title }}</a>
          {% if n.impact %}<span class="impact {{ n.impact }}">{{ n.impact_label or n.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="meta">
          {% if n.time_ago %}<span class="time-ago">{{ n.time_ago }}</span>{% endif %}
          {% if n.source %}<span class="dot">·</span>{{ n.source }}{% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if n.summary %}<div class="summary">{{ n.summary }}</div>{% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% if macro.indicators %}
  <section>
    <h2>
      📊 국내 시장 지표
      {% if macro.indicators_impact %}
      <span class="macro-mood {{ macro.indicators_impact }}">
        {% if macro.indicators_impact == 'positive' %}🟢 우호적
        {% elif macro.indicators_impact == 'negative' %}🔴 부담
        {% else %}🟡 혼조{% endif %}
      </span>
      {% endif %}
    </h2>
    <div class="indicators">
      {% for ind in macro.indicators %}
      <div class="indicator {{ ind.impact or ind.direction or 'neutral' }}">
        <div class="name">{{ ind.name }}</div>
        <div class="value">{{ ind.value }}</div>
        {% if ind.change %}
        <div class="change {{ ind.direction or '' }}">
          <span class="arrow">{% if ind.direction == 'up' %}▲{% elif ind.direction == 'down' %}▼{% endif %}</span>{{ ind.change }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  {% if macro.overnight %}
  <section>
    <h2>
      🌙 간밤 해외 시장
      {% if macro.overnight_impact %}
      <span class="macro-mood {{ macro.overnight_impact }}">
        {% if macro.overnight_impact == 'positive' %}🟢 우호적
        {% elif macro.overnight_impact == 'negative' %}🔴 부담
        {% else %}🟡 혼조{% endif %}
      </span>
      {% endif %}
    </h2>
    <p class="section-sub">미국 증시 전일 종가 및 주요 원자재/환율</p>
    <div class="indicators">
      {% for ind in macro.overnight %}
      <div class="indicator {{ ind.impact or ind.direction or 'neutral' }}">
        <div class="name">{{ ind.name }}</div>
        <div class="value">{{ ind.value }}</div>
        {% if ind.change %}
        <div class="change {{ ind.direction or '' }}">
          <span class="arrow">{% if ind.direction == 'up' %}▲{% elif ind.direction == 'down' %}▼{% endif %}</span>{{ ind.change }}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </div>
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <section>
    <h2>
      🌏 거시 경제
      {% if macro.overall_impact %}
      <span class="macro-mood {{ macro.overall_impact }}">
        {% if macro.overall_impact == 'positive' %}🟢 한국 증시에 우호적
        {% elif macro.overall_impact == 'negative' %}🔴 한국 증시에 부담
        {% else %}🟡 중립/혼조{% endif %}
      </span>
      {% endif %}
    </h2>
    {% if macro.summary %}<p class="summary">{{ macro.summary }}</p>{% endif %}
    {% if macro.key_points %}
    <ul class="points">
      {% for pt in macro.key_points %}
      <li>
        <div class="point-title">
          <span class="text">{{ pt.point }}</span>
          {% if pt.impact %}<span class="impact {{ pt.impact }}">{{ pt.impact_label or pt.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
        </div>
        {% if pt.detail %}<div class="point-detail">{{ pt.detail }}</div>{% endif %}
        {% if pt.sources %}
        <div class="sources">
          {% for src in pt.sources %}<a href="{{ src.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ src.title }}</a>{% endfor %}
        </div>
        {% endif %}
      </li>
      {% endfor %}
    </ul>
    {% endif %}
  </section>

  {% if sectors %}
  <section>
    <h2>🏭 섹터 흐름</h2>
    {% for sec in sectors %}
    <div style="margin-bottom: 16px;">
      <div style="font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 4px;">
        {{ sec.name }}
        {% if sec.impact %}<span class="impact {{ sec.impact }}">{{ sec.impact_label or sec.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
        {% for s in sec.affected or [] %}<span class="sector-tag">{{ s }}</span>{% endfor %}
      </div>
      {% if sec.summary %}<div class="point-detail">{{ sec.summary }}</div>{% endif %}
      {% if sec.key_points %}
      <ul class="points">
        {% for pt in sec.key_points %}
        <li>
          <div class="point-title">
            <span class="text">{{ pt.point }}</span>
            {% if pt.impact %}<span class="impact {{ pt.impact }}">{{ pt.impact_label or pt.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
          </div>
          {% if pt.detail %}<div class="point-detail">{{ pt.detail }}</div>{% endif %}
          {% if pt.sources %}
          <div class="sources">
            {% for src in pt.sources %}<a href="{{ src.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ src.title }}</a>{% endfor %}
          </div>
          {% endif %}
        </li>
        {% endfor %}
      </ul>
      {% endif %}
    </div>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>
  {% endif %}

  <section>
    <h2>📈 종목별 <span class="section-sub" style="font-size: 13px; margin-left: 4px;">(클릭하면 상세 펼침)</span></h2>
    {% for stock in stocks %}
    <article class="stock">
      <details>
        <summary>
          {% if stock.owner %}<span class="owner-tag">👤 {{ stock.owner }}</span>{% endif %}
          <span class="name">{{ stock.name }}</span>
          <span class="code">{{ stock.code }}{% if stock.market %} · {{ stock.market }}{% endif %}</span>
          {% if stock.price_change_display %}
          <span class="price-change {{ stock.price_direction }}">{{ stock.price_change_display }}</span>
          {% endif %}
          {% if stock.recommendation %}
          <span class="rec {{ stock.recommendation }}">{{ stock.recommendation_label or stock.recommendation }}</span>
          {% endif %}
        </summary>
        <div class="body">
          {% if stock.rationale %}<div class="rec-rationale">{{ stock.rationale }}</div>{% endif %}
          {% if stock.summary %}<p class="stock-summary">{{ stock.summary }}</p>{% endif %}

          {% if stock.key_points %}
          <ul class="points">
            {% for pt in stock.key_points %}
            <li>
              <div class="point-title">
                <span class="text">{{ pt.point }}</span>
                {% if pt.impact %}<span class="impact {{ pt.impact }}">{{ pt.impact_label or pt.impact }}</span>{% endif %}
              </div>
              {% if pt.detail %}<div class="point-detail">{{ pt.detail }}</div>{% endif %}
              {% if pt.sources %}
              <div class="sources">
                {% for src in pt.sources %}<a href="{{ src.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ src.title }}</a>{% endfor %}
              </div>
              {% endif %}
            </li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          {% endif %}

          {% if stock.deep_dive %}
          <div class="deep-dive">
            <h4>🔬 심층 분석</h4>
            {% if stock.deep_dive.business %}
            <div class="dd-block">
              <div class="dd-label">주력 사업·제품</div>
              <div class="dd-body">{{ stock.deep_dive.business }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if stock.deep_dive.market %}
            <div class="dd-block">
              <div class="dd-label">시장성</div>
              <div class="dd-body">{{ stock.deep_dive.market }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if stock.deep_dive.competitors %}
            <div class="dd-block">
              <div class="dd-label">경쟁 구도</div>
              <div class="dd-body">
                {% if stock.deep_dive.competitors is string %}{{ stock.deep_dive.competitors }}
                {% else %}
                <div class="dd-tags">{% for c in stock.deep_dive.competitors %}<span class="dd-tag">{{ c }}</span>{% endfor %}</div>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if stock.deep_dive.research_notes %}
            <div class="dd-block">
              <div class="dd-label">R&D / 논문·특허 동향</div>
              <div class="dd-body">{{ stock.deep_dive.research_notes }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if stock.deep_dive.risks %}
            <div class="dd-block">
              <div class="dd-label">리스크</div>
              <div class="dd-body">{{ stock.deep_dive.risks }}</div>
            </div>
            {% endif %}
            {% if stock.deep_dive.sources %}
            <div class="sources">
              {% for src in stock.deep_dive.sources %}<a href="{{ src.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ src.title }}</a>{% endfor %}
            </div>
            {% endif %}
          </div>
          {% endif %}

          {% if stock.disclosures %}
          <h4>공시</h4>
          <ul class="disclosures">
            {% for d in stock.disclosures %}
            <li><a href="{{ d.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ d.title }}</a>{% if d.date %}<span class="date">{{ d.date }}</span>{% endif %}</li>
            {% endfor %}
          </ul>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
      </details>
    </article>
    {% endfor %}
  </section>

  <footer>
    <div class="disclaimer">
      <strong>⚠️ 투자 유의:</strong> 본 리포트는 AI가 공개 뉴스·공시·웹 자료를 종합해 자동 생성한
      개인 참고용이며, 투자 자문·권유가 아닙니다. 투자 판단과 책임은 전적으로 본인에게 있습니다.
      '풀매수/매수/존버/매도/풀매도' 의견은 AI의 단기 뉴스 흐름 해석일 뿐이며, 종목의 내재가치나
      장기 전망을 반영하지 않습니다.
    </div>
    <p>k-ant-daily · 자동 생성 리포트 · <a href="https://github.com/yummyummyummy/k-ant-daily" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub</a></p>
  </footer>
</main>
</body>
</html>
